headline: 2 Popular AI Stocks to Sell Before They Drop 50% and 69%, According to Wall Street Analysts
summary: Palantir and Super Micro Computer have returned 1,900% and 480%, respectively, since early 2023, but certain analysts believe the stocks are overvalued today.  Palantir trades at such a rich valuation that its share price could decline 66% and it would still be the most expensive stock in the S&P 500.  Supermicro has reduced its full-year revenue guidance twice in as many quarters, and increased competition is pressuring its profitability.
